  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContentItem.Contenttype
    The MIME type of the content.
    ContentItem.Language
    The language identifier (two-letter ISO 639-1 identifier) for the language of the content item.
    Profile.ProcessedLanguage
    The language model that was used to process the input.
    ProfileOptions.AcceptLanguage
    The desired language of the response.
    ProfileOptions.ContentLanguage
    The language of the input text for the request: Arabic, English, Japanese, Korean, or Spanish.
    Trait.Category
    The category of the characteristic: `personality` for Big Five personality characteristics, `needs` for Needs, and `values` for Values.
    Warning.WarningId
    The identifier of the warning message.
